description: Celebrate a goal - or anything else - with a classic audio "GOOOOOL" sound.  Try different languages too (Currently supports French and Spanish)
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Audio Goal for a goal
Alexa, ask Audio Goal for a French Goal
Alexa, ask Audio Goal for supported languages
name: Audio Goal
